headline: Huge News for Dutch Bros Stock
summary: Dutch Bros (NYSE: BROS) has bucked this trend.  Dutch Bros is coming for the coffee competition and proved yet again with these recent earnings results that it is a force to be reckoned with in the food and drink sector.  Let's take a closer look at these third-quarter earnings and see whether Dutch Bros stock is a buy today.
